      + [proposal] is not integrated ThinkAbout candidate to inspect how pressure and impact signals should route into deeper SOP records
      + [outside] is outside remains causal proof, hidden internals, worker edits, repository control, external examples, and direct trust
      + [caution] is keep pressure and impact as attention signals until Codex validates evidence and integration
      + [next_step] is Codex validates this proposal and decides whether to draft a deeper ThinkAbout record

    Final check before answering:
    Line 1 must start with &.
    Lines 2 through 9 must use exactly this operator form: two spaces, +, space, [field], space, is, space, value.
    Do not replace is with verbs such as includes, separates, reminds, lists, or contains.
    Use ASCII only; avoid curly quotes, nonbreaking hyphens, and special punctuation.
    Include the literal terms pressure, impact, evidence, outside, not integrated, SensitivityScan, SOPAwarenessNode, ThinkAbout, and term correlation.
